(22, 'news\\September2020\\mK4PsmvyxlKlgpNMZqnZ.jpg', 'Free Up Counter Space with These Small Kitchen Organization Ideas', 'We hope you like the products we recommend. Just so you are aware, Freshome may collect a share of sales from the links on this page.', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <img src=\"http://localhost/Shopping-FPT/public//storage/news/September2020/shutterstock_708218071-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"741\" height=\"495\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 21px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #212121;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">We hope you like the products we recommend. Just so you are aware, Freshome may collect a share of sales from the links on this page.&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 21px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #212121;\">Is&nbsp;cooking and entertaining in your small kitchen difficult? A&nbsp;studio-size kitchen is a challenge to work in,&nbsp;but a few&nbsp;small kitchen organization ideas and a couple of&nbsp;hours of your time can turn your teeny kitchen into a modern, minimalist dream for cooking and celebrating.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 21px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #212121;\">We&rsquo;ve got five inspiring, small kitchens for you that rock. They&rsquo;re full of ideas on how you can declutter your kitchen in&nbsp;fresh, new ways. We&rsquo;ve also included some small kitchen organization products&nbsp;that will help you reclaim or add new counter space and find a home for all the clutter that likes to hang out on your counters.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2rem; font-family: \'RV Montserrat\', helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.875rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #424242;\">1. Light, bright and industrial small kitchen</h2>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 21px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #212121;\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.625rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://freshome.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/industrial.jpg\" alt=\"small kitchen ideas to get rid of clutter - freshome.com\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 21px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #212121;\">Shop These Products Now:&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; transition: color 0.25s ease 0s;\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/s?k=Kitchen+wall+mount+cutlery+hanger&amp;_encoding=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;linkCode=ur2&amp;linkId=bd26dda288ce51543754c194129cdca5&amp;tag=freshome-kitchen-20&amp;ref=nb_sb_noss\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Cutlery Holder</a>&nbsp;&ndash;&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; transition: color 0.25s ease 0s;\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/s?k=kitchen+utensil+wall+shelf&amp;_encoding=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;linkCode=ur2&amp;linkId=78e30fd97796c582a8b85b966417c1ba&amp;tag=freshome-kitchen-20&amp;ref=nb_sb_noss\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Utensil Self</a>&nbsp;&ndash;&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; transition: color 0.25s ease 0s;\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Utopia-Kitchen-Utensil-Holder-Container/dp/B01DVG3PCE/ref=sr_1_2?keywords=kitchen+Spoon+Holder&amp;qid=1583985790&amp;sr=8-2&amp;_encoding=UTF8&amp;tag=freshome-kitchen-20&amp;linkCode=ur2&amp;linkId=aa464e5a905a8e715b2769c47ab8c817&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Spoon Holder</a>&nbsp;&ndash;&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; transition: color 0.25s ease 0s;\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/s?k=cooking+Pan&amp;_encoding=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;linkCode=ur2&amp;linkId=8d131dbe4e724340d3f8e0c9c0070b1f&amp;tag=freshome-kitchen-20&amp;ref=nb_sb_noss_2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Cooking Pan</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 21px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #212121;\">First off, consider painting&nbsp;your kitchen in a light, bright white to freshen it up. Or cover the dark, outdated walls or cabinet doors with a fresh, new&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; transition: color 0.25s ease 0s;\" href=\"https://freshome.com/removable-wallpaper/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">removable wallpaper</a>.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 21px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #212121;\">Next, it&rsquo;s&nbsp;time&nbsp;to throw out those cans of hearts of palm you never use and decide what else stays or goes. Once you&rsquo;ve got a good idea of how much you&rsquo;re working with, it&rsquo;s time to find a home for everything that&rsquo;s left.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 21px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #212121;\">Store what isn&rsquo;t attractive in your cabinets. The rest of the items can display on new, industrial, restaurant-style shelves, bars and hooks like in the photo above.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 21px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #212121;\">Shop These Products Now:&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; transition: color 0.25s ease 0s;\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/s?k=magnetic+knife+strip&amp;_encoding=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;crid=25CU8YX64CY9Q&amp;linkCode=ur2&amp;linkId=8e16e45a5e9be3c06360f9e9d99c3889&amp;sprefix=magnetic+kni%2Caps%2C424&amp;tag=freshome-kitchen-20&amp;ref=nb_sb_ss_i_1_12\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Magnetic Knife Strip</a>&nbsp;&ndash;&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; transition: color 0.25s ease 0s;\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/s?k=wall+mounted+bowl+rack&amp;_encoding=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;linkCode=ur2&amp;linkId=bd700c31b3b8b934e9fab9c3d6dd492e&amp;tag=freshome-kitchen-20&amp;ref=nb_sb_noss_2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Bowl Rack</a></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2rem; font-family: \'RV Montserrat\', helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.875rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #424242;\">2. Small modern kitchen featuring a modular, rolling island</h2>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 21px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #212121;\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.625rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://freshome.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/rolling.jpg\" alt=\"rolling island ideas for a small kitchen - freshome.com\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 21px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #212121;\">Shop These Products Now:&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; transition: color 0.25s ease 0s;\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/s?k=Kitchen+Cart&amp;_encoding=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;linkCode=ur2&amp;linkId=413bfe68ea7821490cf9347f4a834eff&amp;tag=freshome-kitchen-20&amp;ref=nb_sb_noss_2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Kitchen Cart</a>&nbsp;&ndash;&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; transition: color 0.25s ease 0s;\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/s?k=Bar+Stool&amp;_encoding=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;linkCode=ur2&amp;linkId=7e114ac9333119384d89bc8af6f2d826&amp;tag=freshome-kitchen-20&amp;ref=nb_sb_noss_2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Bar Stool</a>&nbsp;&ndash;&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; transition: color 0.25s ease 0s;\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/s?k=Fruit+Bowl&amp;_encoding=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;linkCode=ur2&amp;linkId=69c68dfdaa9a6f200e0d53c15e807b64&amp;tag=freshome-kitchen-20&amp;ref=nb_sb_noss_2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Fruit Bowl</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 21px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #212121;\">In many small kitchens&nbsp;there isn&rsquo;t much counter space to work with. Basic appliances like a coffee maker or microwave can eat up the little space you have. There&nbsp;are&nbsp;solutions. Choose appliances that can be wall-mounted or under-cabinet mounted. Or add a heavy-duty wall-mounted shelf to hold heavy appliances like a microwave.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 21px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #212121;\">A&nbsp;small kitchen island can add&nbsp;extra counter space as well as storage &mdash; and even a&nbsp;breakfast bar.&nbsp;Small, round or square islands work better in smaller square spaces. Consider a longer narrow island for a rectangular space. A sofa console on wheels would be a great idea in a longer, galley kitchen. You can roll it into a kitchen as needed and then put it back behind your sofa when done.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 21px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #212121;\">Butcher blocks or bar carts are other great options because they often come with wheels to&nbsp;roll your island out of the way. A&nbsp;taller&nbsp;cart works well with barstools.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 21px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #212121;\">Shop These Products Now:&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; transition: color 0.25s ease 0s;\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/s?k=Bar+Stool&amp;_encoding=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;linkCode=ur2&amp;linkId=847fbfaf72f3a33af87352f3801aaea3&amp;tag=freshome-kitchen-20&amp;ref=nb_sb_noss_2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Bar Stool</a>&nbsp;&ndash;&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; transition: color 0.25s ease 0s;\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/s?k=Kitchen+Cart&amp;_encoding=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;linkCode=ur2&amp;linkId=f6724f2585cffe2a98d14ed3be07ae6b&amp;tag=freshome-kitchen-20&amp;ref=nb_sb_noss_2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Kitchen Cart</a></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2rem; font-family: \'RV Montserrat\', helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.875rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #424242;\">3. A contemporary small kitchen with&nbsp;floating wall shelves for storage</h2>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 21px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #212121;\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.625rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://freshome.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/floating-ledges.jpg\" alt=\"small kitchen storage ideas - freshome.com\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 21px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #212121;\">Shop These Products Now:&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; transition: color 0.25s ease 0s;\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/s?k=floating+shelves+for+kitchen&amp;_encoding=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;crid=CCUV9544S5M4&amp;linkCode=ur2&amp;linkId=f4c3faa40c12c463eea252e986a1357f&amp;sprefix=Floating+shelves+for+ki%2Caps%2C436&amp;tag=freshome-kitchen-20&amp;ref=nb_sb_ss_i_1_23\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Wall Shelves</a>&nbsp;&ndash;&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; transition: color 0.25s ease 0s;\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/s?k=Range+Hood&amp;_encoding=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;linkCode=ur2&amp;linkId=da1fe883080fb379f4bb943a3fa91c1f&amp;tag=freshome-kitchen-20&amp;ref=nb_sb_noss_2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Range Hood</a>&nbsp;&ndash;&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; transition: color 0.25s ease 0s;\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/s?k=Toaster&amp;_encoding=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;linkCode=ur2&amp;linkId=32e63c6cca37227ed913bad85e009958&amp;tag=freshome-kitchen-20&amp;ref=nb_sb_noss_2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Toaster</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 21px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #212121;\">If you don&rsquo;t have enough kitchen cabinets but plenty of wall space, a clean, contemporary way to free up your kitchen counters is to display and store items on&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; transition: color 0.25s ease 0s;\" href=\"https://freshome.com/inspiration/10-floating-shelves-to-create-contemporary-wall-display/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">cool floating shelves</a>&nbsp;or ledges like the kitchen above.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 21px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #212121;\">Want to give your kitchen a high-design look like the photo? Group the items by color and add some art objects or framed photos. Leave some areas of the ledges empty so they don&rsquo;t look too cluttered.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 21px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #212121;\">Another great design choice in the image above is the use of mirror on the backsplash. Add some mirror to a section of your wall behind the countertop to expand the space and reflect more light.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 21px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #212121;\">Shop These Products Now:&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; transition: color 0.25s ease 0s;\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/s?k=wall+floating+shelves+for+kitchen&amp;_encoding=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;linkCode=ur2&amp;linkId=03cd6129dd5a29998c9da6c585007179&amp;tag=freshome-kitchen-20&amp;ref=nb_sb_noss\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Floating Shelves</a></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2rem; font-family: \'RV Montserrat\', helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.875rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #424242;\">4. Small kitchen organization ideas featuring&nbsp;bookcases</h2>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 21px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #212121;\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.625rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://freshome.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/bookcases.jpg\" alt=\"small apartment kitchen ideas and studio kitchen storage ideas - freshome.com\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 21px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #212121;\">Shop These Products Now:&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; transition: color 0.25s ease 0s;\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/s?k=cooking+pan+hangers&amp;_encoding=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;crid=1L9JOBN7QXDBJ&amp;linkCode=ur2&amp;linkId=0f0b86355cfb5ebf90e874669cc12bb3&amp;sprefix=Cooking+Pan+Han%2Caps%2C972&amp;tag=freshome-kitchen-20&amp;ref=nb_sb_ss_i_3_15\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Cooking Pan Hanger</a>&nbsp;&ndash;&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; transition: color 0.25s ease 0s;\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/s?k=Spoon+Holder&amp;_encoding=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;linkCode=ur2&amp;linkId=c3dd6f6f2d27c2fb741f282f82520220&amp;tag=freshome-kitchen-20&amp;ref=nb_sb_noss_2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Spoon Holder</a>&nbsp;&ndash;&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; transition: color 0.25s ease 0s;\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/s?k=Toaster&amp;_encoding=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;linkCode=ur2&amp;linkId=ab4b7c1598aaf1670ea4d21d79d020dd&amp;tag=freshome-kitchen-20&amp;ref=nb_sb_noss_2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Toaster</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 21px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #212121;\">Adding or replacing kitchen cabinets can be expensive. And if you rent, the project may not even be allowed. Why not buy some good, inexpensive bookcases and make a storage wall for all your kitchen items?</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 21px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #212121;\">Look for taller but narrow bookcases and mix and match doors to hide some of the items. Or a selection of baskets can serve as drawers in your bookcases, ready to catch all the smaller items and linens.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 21px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #212121;\">Another interesting small kitchen idea in the image above is the hooks over the window for hanging&nbsp;pots and pans.&nbsp;Pots and pans take up a lot of space and hanging them from a pot rack or hooks is a good way to free up a cabinet or counter.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 21px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #212121;\">Shop These Products Now:&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; transition: color 0.25s ease 0s;\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/s?k=cooking+pan+hangers&amp;_encoding=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;crid=3V7MFFXDJKYJY&amp;linkCode=ur2&amp;linkId=cdf4735f284d8daf67b8e00dcdf765a2&amp;sprefix=cooking+pan+%2Caps%2C612&amp;tag=freshome-kitchen-20&amp;ref=nb_sb_ss_i_7_12\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Cooking Pan Wall Mount Rail</a></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2rem; font-family: \'RV Montserrat\', helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.875rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #424242;\">5. A minimalist kitchen that brings many&nbsp;small apartment organization ideas together</h2>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 21px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #212121;\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.625rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://freshome.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/modern-storing.jpg\" alt=\"clutter-free small kitchen decorating - freshome.com\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 21px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #212121;\">Shop These Products Now:&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; transition: color 0.25s ease 0s;\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/s?k=glass+holder+wall+mounted&amp;_encoding=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;crid=2BZ8UDTFW6V3U&amp;linkCode=ur2&amp;linkId=3833ecb0ff482be0234a4fc97b28b1a3&amp;sprefix=Glass+holder+%2Caps%2C425&amp;tag=freshome-kitchen-20&amp;ref=nb_sb_ss_i_4_13\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Glass Holder</a>&nbsp;&ndash;&nbsp;<a sty