(26, 'news\\September2020\\GqzIRskIaelXK1GBRvJ9.jpg', 'DIY Stump Removal: Tips and Tricks', 'Did you have to cut down a tree from your yard due to a storm, natural disaster, root growth, or an infestation? The tree stumps left behind can be an eyesore. If you’ve got some free time and don’t mind flexing your muscles to get the job done, you can avoid costly stump removal services and take care of the project yourself.', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img src=\"http://localhost/Shopping-FPT/public//storage/news/September2020/GqzIRskIaelXK1GBRvJ91.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"740\" height=\"493\" /></p>\r\n<div id=\"contentContainer\" class=\"post__content\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 1.3125rem; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 41.875rem; color: #212121; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 1.3125rem; vertical-align: baseline;\">Did you have to cut down a tree from your yard due to a storm, natural disaster, root growth, or an infestation? The tree stumps left behind can be an eyesore. If you&rsquo;ve got some free time and don&rsquo;t mind flexing your muscles to get the job done, you can avoid costly stump removal services and take care of the project yourself.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 1.3125rem; vertical-align: baseline;\">While there is more than one stump&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 21px; vertical-align: baseline; transition: color 0.25s ease 0s; color: inherit; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://www.nycgovparks.org/services/forestry/dead-tree-removal\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">removal process</a>, the following guide shows you the easiest way to get it done yourself. Before putting your saw to wood, make sure you&rsquo;re wearing proper safety equipment and clothing. This includes safety glasses, safety gloves, earplugs, long trousers, a jacket, and proper boots. Consult with a&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 21px; vertical-align: baseline; transition: color 0.25s ease 0s; color: inherit; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://www.lowes.com/n/how-to/operate-a-chainsaw\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">local home improvement expert</a>&nbsp;if you&rsquo;re unsure about proper chainsaw operation and safety procedures.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2rem; font-family: \'RV Montserrat\', helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.875rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #424242;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;8 steps to DIY stump removal</h2>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.5625rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2rem; font-family: \'RV Montserrat\', helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.3125rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #424242;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Step 1: Cut down as much of the tree stump as you can</h3>\r\n<div class=\"post__content\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 1.3125rem; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 41.875rem; color: #212121; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 1.3125rem; vertical-align: baseline;\">Cut down the stump as low as you can. The only way to really do this effectively is with a chainsaw. We recommend wearing steel-toed boots, work gloves, earplugs, and eye protection while using a chainsaw.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5625rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2rem; font-family: \'RV Montserrat\', helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.3125rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #424242;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Step 2: Drill holes into the remainder of the stump</h3>\r\n<div class=\"post__content\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 1.3125rem; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 41.875rem; color: #212121; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 1.3125rem; vertical-align: baseline;\">Drill from the top down, with every hole about 2 to 3 inches apart and about 8 to 10 inches deep. Drill holes from the sides of the stump as well, aiming to intersect with the holes coming down from the top. Make sure to use a drill bit that&rsquo;s 3/8 of an inch in diameter.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5625rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2rem; font-family: \'RV Montserrat\', helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.3125rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #424242;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Step 3: Apply the chemicals</h3>\r\n<div class=\"post__content\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 1.3125rem; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 41.875rem; color: #212121; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 1.3125rem; vertical-align: baseline;\">Once you&rsquo;re done drilling the holes, pour the stump removal chemicals down each of the top holes. When choosing a tree stump removal chemical, fine granules are much easier to use. Products that come in powder form tend to clog at the very top of the holes, while&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 21px; vertical-align: baseline; transition: color 0.25s ease 0s; color: inherit; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Spectracide-Stump-Remover-Granules-1-Pound/dp/B004GVYXKC/ref=sr_1_5?crid=1D0P3E6TT2WQ3&amp;keywords=bromide+stump-out&amp;qid=1585611997&amp;sprefix=bromide+stump%2Caps%2C225&amp;sr=8-5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">products made with fine granules</a>&nbsp;usually roll right down to the bottom.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5625rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2rem; font-family: \'RV Montserrat\', helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.3125rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #424242;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Step 4: Pour water into the holes</h3>\r\n<div class=\"post__content\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 1.3125rem; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 41.875rem; color: #212121; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 1.3125rem; vertical-align: baseline;\">After each hole is filled with a stump removal chemical, add water as per the instructions that come with the chemical you purchased.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 1.3125rem; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 900; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 21px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Pro tip:&nbsp;</strong>Pouring too much water can dilute the stump chemicals, which could have a negative impact on how well the product works. Always measure your water precisely and follow the written instructions closely.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5625rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2rem; font-family: \'RV Montserrat\', helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.3125rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #424242;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Step 5: Cover the stump</h3>\r\n<div class=\"post__content\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 1.3125rem; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 41.875rem; color: #212121; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 1.3125rem; vertical-align: baseline;\">The stump removal process usually takes several weeks depending on what chemical is used. To protect children and animals, make sure the stump is covered at all times. Any exposure to the stump without taking precautions could be dangerous. Cover the stump with a tarp and pieces of scrap wood, rocks, or bricks. Periodically check the stump to see how much effect the chemicals have had and that the covering is still in place.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5625rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2rem; font-family: \'RV Montserrat\', helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.3125rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #424242;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Step 6: Soak the stump with kerosene</h3>\r\n<div class=\"post__content\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 1.3125rem; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 41.875rem; color: #212121; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 1.3125rem; vertical-align: baseline;\">Once the stump looks more like a sponge or mulch and breaks apart easily, it&rsquo;s time to break out the kerosene. Soak the stump and let it sit for a few more weeks. Kerosene is used at this point because you won&rsquo;t be able to manually remove the stump in its current state.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5625rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2rem; font-family: \'RV Montserrat\', helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.3125rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #424242;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Step 7: Set the stump on fire</h3>\r\n<div class=\"post__content\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 1.3125rem; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 41.875rem; color: #212121; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 1.3125rem; vertical-align: baseline;\">First, check with your town about any restrictions to open fires in your area. If all is well, it&rsquo;s time to set the stump on fire. After a few weeks, uncover your stump, remove any surrounding debris, and create a ring of rocks or bricks around the stump. Add some kindling if needed and set it on fire. Keep a hose, a fire extinguisher, or baking soda nearby in case the fire spreads too far.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 1.3125rem; vertical-align: baseline;\">The fire should go out when the stump is totally gone, leaving only a hole in the ground where it used to be. Be prepared: it can take days for the embers to burn down. Never leave the initial fire unattended and make sure there are no people or animals nearby who could get hurt.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5625rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2rem; font-family: \'RV Montserrat\', helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.3125rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #424242;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Step 8: Fill the hole</h3>\r\n<div class=\"post__content\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 1.3125rem; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 41.875rem; color: #212121; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 1.3125rem; vertical-align: baseline;\">Once the fire is out and the stump is gone, pull out any remaining roots and&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 21px; vertical-align: baseline; transition: color 0.25s ease 0s; color: inherit; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://www.mymove.com/lawn-care/guides/types-of-grass/\">fill the hole with sod</a>. Pack the sod firmly and block off the area for another week as a precaution.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.875rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2rem; font-family: \'RV Montserrat\', helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.875rem; vertical-align: baseline; color: #424242;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Products and tools you&rsquo;ll need for tree stump removal</h2>\r\n<div class=\"post__content\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 2.0625rem; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', georgia, sans-serif; font-size: 1.3125rem; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 41.875rem; color: #212121; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webk